},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"rethrows","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SM5IndexQa","text":"Index"}],"url":"/documentation/swift/emptycollection/partition(by:)-37csa","type":"topic"},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/EmptyCollection":{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/EmptyCollection","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EmptyCollection"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"EmptyCollection"}],"type":"topic","url":"/documentation/swift/emptycollection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection whose element type is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Element"},{"type":"text","text":" but that is always empty."}],"title":"EmptyCollection","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/MutableCollection/Index":{"required":true,"role":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/mutablecollection/index","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/MutableCollection/Index","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"Index","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"associatedtype"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Index","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/MutableCollection/Element":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/MutableCollection/Element","fragments":[{"text":"associatedtype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Element"}],"url":"/documentation/swift/mutablecollection/element","title":"Element","required":true},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift":{"type":"topic","title":"Swift","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Build apps using a powerful open language."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift","role":"collection","id